97
00:05:42,737 --> 00:05:46,942
for those who lack dexterity to handle small motions.

98
00:05:46,942 --> 00:05:50,465
So you put that together, it's important for sensitivity

99
00:05:50,465 --> 00:05:52,568
to both go up and down.

100
00:05:53,387 --> 00:05:59,708
