00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:12,471
Maybe I don't need infinite stamina and visibility,

302
00:17:12,471 --> 00:17:15,952
but that at least means that when I have this fast moving jumps,

303
00:17:15,952 --> 00:17:18,614
I might be able to react in time.

304
00:17:18,614 --> 00:17:20,815
I will say that that was absolutely not true.

305
00:17:20,815 --> 00:17:23,416
Oh my God, this game is so hard, so fast.

306
00:17:23,416 --> 00:17:26,137
And I kept jumping and blowing up

307
00:17:26,137 --> 00:17:28,418
because as soon as you touch a spike, you are dead.

308
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:31,642
unless you turn on invulnerability.

309
00:17:31,642 --> 00:17:33,404
At that point, you touch the spikes,

310
00:17:33,404 --> 00:17:34,325
you're not instantly dead,

311
00:17:34,325 --> 00:17:35,726
and you can figure out,

312
00:17:35,726 --> 00:17:38,229
so what am I supposed to do now?

313
00:17:38,229 --> 00:17:40,792
And you don't have to start the whole screen over.

314
00:17:40,792 --> 00:17:42,714
It is wonderful that either way,

315
00:17:42,714 --> 00:17:44,136
you only have to redo a screen.

316
00:17:44,917 --> 00:17:50,600
But overall, I didn't think I was going to need this, and it turns out I very desperately did.

317
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:57,144
And that meant that I played. Now, if I didn't have those options, I would have hit a wall

318
00:17:57,144 --> 00:18:02,467
very, very early that I would not have been able to get past. At that point, I only played a couple

319
00:18:02,467 --> 00:18:08,050
percentage points of the game. So this means that I can play and experience the majority of the game

320
00:18:08,050 --> 00:18:11,532
and story. And that's what really matters, is having an experience.

