00:19:09,693 --> 00:19:13,114
and I really don't want to shoot my friends. That's really not the goal here.

339
00:19:13,114 --> 00:19:16,715
So I greatly appreciate what options exist to turn it off,

340
00:19:16,715 --> 00:19:19,296
or if it's just not there in the first place like it is with Diablo.

341
00:19:19,296 --> 00:19:25,898
Um, yeah, I love this game so much. I love games in general. I've played the

342
00:19:25,898 --> 00:19:27,738
majority of the games we have here and then some.

