00:19:27,738 --> 00:19:33,180
Um, how much I play varies on my hands and I'm very careful about it,

344
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:35,660
but I am a very much a hardcore gamer.

345
00:19:38,629 --> 00:19:42,621
Can chat means less typing, so when you're playing with your friends,

346
00:19:42,621 --> 00:19:46,312
friendly fire is not the only thing that matters. Communication matters too.

347
00:19:47,413 --> 00:19:50,495
Now, CanChat's wonderful for so many reasons.

348
00:19:50,495 --> 00:19:53,417
It means that I don't have to do extensive typing,

349
00:19:53,417 --> 00:19:54,978
but I can still get the point across.

